snippet.title: Ducky's Delivery Service - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Ducky's Delivery Service is releasing in July 2023! Wishlist it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2080970/Duckys_Delivery_Service/
Wishlist it on itch.io: https://ctmatthews.itch.io/duckys-delivery-service

In Ducky's Delivery Service, you are a duck who uses a propeller backpack to fly around and deliver mail. Learn to fly, grow your delivery business, fulfill special delivery requests from other ducks, and earn time attack ranks and high scores.
